# Raw pasta pesto

## Pasta

3 spiralised zucchini (medium)

## Sauce

80g Fresh basil
1/3C Olive oil
1C Nuts (half pine nuts, half cashew)
5 Garlic Cloves
1/3C Nutritional yeast
1/2tsp Salt
1/2tsp Black pepper


## Topping

60g Capers
3 Pink radish
3 Big avocadoes
100g Tomatoes OR 30g Sundried tomatoes
30g spinach
30g fresh basil

## Instructions

Spiralise the zucchini. Blend the sauce, pour it on the zucchini. Add topping.
